uanet.com/book/2019-07/18/c_1210201764.htm \u8457\u540d\u5267\u4f5c\u5bb6\u82cf\u53d4\u9633\u75c5\u901d \u7559\u4e0b15\u4e07\u5b57\u300a\u4e2d\u56fd\u8bfb\u672c\u300b\u4f20\u540e\u4eba] {{in lang|zh}}</ref>\n*[[John Tanton]], 85, American anti-immigration activist.<ref>[https://www.freep.com/story/news/local/michigan/2019/07/18/anti-immigrant-john-tanton-dies/1764377001/ Anti-immigrant leader Dr. John Tanton of Michigan dies at 85]</ref>\n*[[Bill Vitt]], American drummer.<ref>[http://exclaim.ca/music/article/r_i_p_jerry_garcia_drummer_bill_vitt R.I.P. Jerry Garcia Drummer Bill Vitt]</ref>\n\n===17===\n*[[Andrea Camilleri]], 93, Italian writer ([[Salvo Montalbano]]) and television writer (''[[Le inchieste del commissario Maigret]]''), complications from a heart attack.<ref>[https://www.ansa.it/amp/sito/notizie/cultura/2019/07/17/andrea-camilleri-e-morto-_2b738047-4a64-4275-8134-d756f42e0b6d.html Andrea Camilleri \u00e8 morto, addio al pap\u00e0 di Montalbano] {{in lang|it}}</ref>\n*[[Ismail Changezi]], 65, Pakistani actor.<ref>[https://arynews.tv/en/ismail-changezi-passes-away/ Veteran actor Ismail Changezi passes away]</ref>\n*[[Warren Cole]], 78, New Zealand rower, Olympic champion ([[Rowing at the 1968 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's coxed four|1968]]).<ref>[https://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/other-sports/114302661/new-zealand-rowing-olympic-gold-medallist-warren-cole-dies-aged-78 New Zealand rowing Olympic gold medallist Warren Cole dies, aged 78]</ref>\n*[[Swarup Dutta]], 78, Indian actor (''[[Apanjan]]'', ''[[Uphaar]]'', ''[[Andha Atit]]'').<ref>[https://www.newsnation.in/entertainment/regional-cinema/veteran-bengali-actor-swarup-dutta-dies-at-78-article-231058.html Veteran Bengali actor Swarup Dutta dies at 78]</ref>\n*[[Pumpsie Green]], 85, American baseball player ([[Boston Red Sox]], [[New York Mets]]).<ref>[https://patch.com/massachusetts/boston/pumpsie-green-first-black-red-sox-player-dies-85 Pumpsie Green, First Black Red Sox Player, Dies At 85]</ref>\n*[[Nikola