.es/politica/diputado-exministro-uruguayo-Jaime-Trobo_0_924257568.html El diputado y exministro uruguayo Jaime Trobo fallece a causa de un c\u00e1ncer] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*[[Trudy (gorilla)|Trudy]], 63, American gorilla, world's oldest gorilla in captivity.<ref>[https://www.nwahomepage.com/news/trudy-believed-the-oldest-gorilla-in-captivity-dies-at-63/ Trudy, believed the oldest gorilla in captivity, dies at 63]</ref>\n*[[Manfred Uhlig]], 91, German actor (''[[Hands Up or I'll Shoot]]'').<ref>[https://www.spiegel.de/kultur/tv/manfred-uhlig-ein-kessel-buntes-kabarettist-ist-tot-a-1278860.html Manfred Uhlig ist tot] {{in lang|de}}</ref>\n*[[Roger Warren]], 75, Canadian miner and murderer.<ref>[https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/north/roger-warren-giant-mine-bomber-dead-1.5341921 Giant Mine bomber Roger Warren dead at 75]</ref>\n\n===25===\n*[[Giorgio Arlorio]], 90, Italian film director and screenwriter (''[[The Shortest Day]]'', ''[[Ogro]]'', ''[[Once Upon a Crime]]'').<ref>[https://www.repubblica.it/spettacoli/cinema/2019/07/25/news/giorgio_arlorio-232021043/ \u00c8 morto Giorgio Arlorio, sceneggiatore per Pontecorvo e Loy] {{in lang|it}}</ref>\n*[[Farouk al-Fishawy]], 67, Egyptian actor (''[[The Suspect (1981 film)|The Suspect]]''), cancer.<ref>[https://www.thenational.ae/arts-culture/film/egyptian-actor-farouk-al-fishawy-dies-aged-67-following-cancer-battle-1.890488 Egyptian actor Farouk Al Fishawy dies, aged 67, following cancer battle]</ref>\n*[[Simon Bendall]], 82, English numismatist.<ref>[https://coinsweekly.com/simon-bendall-1937-2019/ Simon Bendall]</ref>\n*[[Anner Bylsma]], 85, Dutch cellist.<ref>[https://theviolinchannel.com/dutch-cellist-anner-bylsma-died-passed-away-85-obituary/ Dutch Cellist Anner Bylsma Has Died \u2013 Aged 85]</ref>\n*[[Peter Edwards (vexillologist)|Peter Edwards]], 88, British-born Canadian [[vexillologist]].<ref>[https://fotw.info/flags/xm-pbe.html In Memory of Peter Edwards (1931-2019)]</ref>\n*[[Beji Caid Essebsi]], 92, Tunisian p