30/walter-fiers-pionier-van-de-vlaamse-biotechnologie-is-overlede/ Walter Fiers, pionier van de Vlaamse biotechnologie, is overleden] {{in lang|nl}}</ref>\n*[[Eduardo G\u00f3mez (actor)|Eduardo G\u00f3mez]], 68, Spanish actor and comedian (''[[Aqu\u00ed no hay quien viva]]'', ''[[La que se avecina]]'', ''[[Butterfly's Tongue]]''), cancer.<ref>[https://www.huffingtonpost.es/entry/muere-eduardo-gomez-actor-de-aqui-no-hay-quien-viva-a-los-68-anos_es_5d3d57f7e4b0ef792e0d7607 Muere Eduardo G\u00f3mez, actor de 'Aqu\u00ed No Hay Quien Viva' y 'La Que Se Avecina', a los 68 a\u00f1os] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*[[George Hilton (actor)|George Hilton]], 85, Uruguayan actor (''[[The Masked Man Against the Pirates]]'', ''[[The Brute and the Beast]]'', ''[[Man Called Invincible]]'').<ref>[https://www.iltempo.it/home/2019/07/29/news/morto-george-hilton-mito-spaghetti-western-cinema-college-tresette-alleluja-thriller-abbronzatissimi-1193367/ Addio a George Hilton, icona dello spaghetti western] {{in lang|it}}</ref>\n*[[Peter Bonu Johnson]], 56, Gambian football player and  manager ([[Gambia national football team|national team]]).<ref>[https://gambiaff.org/ex-gambia-coach-peter-bonu-johnson-dies/ Ex-Gambia Coach Peter Bonu Johnson Dies]</ref>\n*[[Vladimir Kara-Murza Sr.]], 59, Russian journalist and TV host, co-founder of [[NTV (Russia)|NTV]].<ref>[http://micetimes.asia/died-in-moscow-the-journalist-kara-murza/ Died in Moscow the journalist Kara-Murza]</ref>\n*[[Li Jisheng]], 76, Chinese aerospace engineer.<ref>[https://cbgc.scol.com.cn/news/162140 \u53c8\u4e00\u201c\u661f\u8fb0\u201d\u9668\u843d\u2026\u2026\u536b\u661f\u6d4b\u63a7\u4e13\u5bb6\u674e\u6d4e\u751f\u9662\u58eb\u53bb\u4e16] {{in lang|zh}}</ref>\n*[[Peter McConnell (footballer)|Peter McConnell]], 82, English footballer ([[Carlisle United F.C.|Carlisle United]], [[Leeds United F.C.|Leeds United]], [[Bradford City A.F.C.|Bradford City]]).<ref>[https://www.newsandstar.co.uk/sport/17801553.tributes-paid-carlisle-united-legend-p