a.it/sito/notizie/cronaca/2019/07/28/morto-ex-parlamentare-cesare-rizzi_08e017f9-ad32-436e-a208-b06bdfc72301.html Morto ex parlamentare Cesare Rizzi] {{in lang|it}}</ref>\n*[[Richard Rosenbaum]], 88, American judge, member of the [[New York Supreme Court]] (1970\u20131972), chairman of the [[New York Republican State Committee]] (1972\u20131977).<ref>[https://www.democratandchronicle.com/story/news/2019/07/29/richard-rosenbaum-former-new-york-state-supreme-court-justice-dies-penfield-ny/1847649001/ Richard Rosenbaum, former state Supreme Court justice, dies]</ref>\n*[[Donkupar Roy]], 64, Indian politician, [[Chief Minister of Meghalaya]] (2008\u20132009), stomach disease.<ref>[https://indianexpress.com/article/north-east-india/meghalaya/meghalaya-assembly-speaker-donkupar-roy-dies-at-64-5858717/ Meghalaya Assembly Speaker Donkupar Roy passes away]</ref>\n*[[Bandar bin Abdulaziz Al Saud]], 96, Saudi royal.<ref>[https://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2019/Jul-29/488585-prince-bandar-elder-brother-of-saudi-king-salman-dies-at-96.ashx Prince Bandar, elder brother of Saudi King Salman, dies at 96]</ref>\n*[[M. K. Seetharam Kulal]], 79, Indian Tulu-Kannada dramatist.<ref>[https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/tulu-playwright-m-k-seetharama-kulal-passes-away/article28737959.ece Tulu playwright MK Seetharama Kulal passes away]</ref>\n*[[Yuu Shimaka]], 70, Japanese voice actor (''[[Kingdom Hearts]]'', ''[[Ergo Proxy]]'', ''[[Code Geass]]'').<ref>[https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-08-05/kingdom-hearts-code-geass-voice-actor-yu-shimaka-passes-away-at-70/.149710 Kingdom Hearts, Code Geass Voice Actor Y\u016b Shimaka Passes Away at 70]</ref>\n*[[Ruth de Souza]], 98, Brazilian actress (''[[The Landowner's Daughter]]'', ''[[Macumba Love]]'', ''[[A Glass of Rage]]''), pneumonia.<ref>[https://g1.globo.com/rj/rio-de-janeiro/noticia/2019/07/28/atriz-ruth-de-souza-morre-no-rio-aos-98-anos.ghtml Atriz Ruth de Souza morre no Rio aos 98 anos] {{in lang|pt}}</ref