ld be in <ref>[url & title]</ref> format, as full citations make the page too slow to load, and too big to edit.\n\n* * * * * * * Please adhere to the guidelines above when adding a name to this article * * * * * * *-->\n\n==July 2019==\n===1===\n*[[Ezzat Abou Aouf]], 70, Egyptian actor, liver and heart failure.<ref>[http://www.arabnews.com/node/1518816 Veteran Egyptian actor Ezzat Abu Auf dies at 70]</ref>\n*[[Joseph Bolangi Egwanga Ediba Tasame]], 81, [[Democratic Republic of the Congo|Congolese]] Roman Catholic prelate, Bishop of [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Budjala|Budjala]] (1974\u20132009).<ref>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bboleet.html Bishop Joseph Bolangi Egwanga Ediba Tasame \u2020]</ref>\n*[[Bob Collymore]], 61, Guyanese-born British telecom executive, CEO of [[Safaricom]] (since 2010), [[acute myeloid leukaemia]].<ref>[https://www.the-star.co.ke/news/2019-07-01-safaricom-boss-bob-collymore-is-dead/ Safaricom boss Bob Collymore is dead]</ref>\n*[[Nikola Dagorov]], 94, Bulgarian Olympic triple jumper ([[Athletics at the 1952 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's triple jump|1952]]).<ref>[https://bgathletic.com/new.php?id=26421 In Memoriam: \u041d\u0430\u043f\u0443\u0441\u043d\u0430 \u043d\u0438 \u0434-\u0440 \u041d\u0438\u043a\u043e\u043b\u0430 \u0414\u0430\u0433\u043e\u0440\u043e\u0432] {{in lang|bg}}</ref>\n*[[Renato Deh\u00f2]], 72, Italian footballer.<ref>[https://www.leccoonline.com/articolo.php?idd=45631&origine=1 E\u2019 scomparso Renato Deh\u00f2: gioc\u00f2 nel Lecco dopo l\u2019Inter] {{in lang|it}}</ref>\n*[[Norman Geisler]], 86, American theologian.<ref>[https://www.christianitytoday.com/news/2019/july/died-apologist-norman-geisler-apologist-seminary-ses-theolo.html Died: Apologist Norman Geisler, Who Didn\u2019t Have \u2018Enough Faith to Be an Atheist\u2019]</ref>\n*[[Osvalda Giardi]], 86, Italian high jumper and pentathlete.<ref>[https://www.quinewspisa.it/san-giuliano-terme-sport-in-lutto-muore-ex-campionessa-italiana.htm Sport, muore ex 