{"title_page": "2020 MFF Charity Cup", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2018}}\n{{Infobox football match\n| title              = 2020 MFF Charity Cup \n| image              =\n| caption            = \n| team1              = [[Shan United F.C.|Shan United]]\n| team1score         = 2\n| team2              =  [[Yangon United F.C.|Yangon United]]\n| team2score         = 1\n| details            = \n| date               = 5 January 2020\n| stadium            = [[Yangon United Sports Complex]]\n| city               = Yangon\n| man_of_the_match1a =  {{flagicon|MYA}} [[Ye Min Thu]]\n| referee            =   Mr. Kyaw Zwal Lwin\n| attendance         =  15.000\n| weather            =   Sunny <br />{{convert|27|\u00b0C|\u00b0F}}\n| previous           = [[2019 MFF Charity Cup|2019]]\n| next               = 2021\n}}\n\nThe '''2020 MFF  Charity Cup''' (also known as the '''2020 MPT Charity Cup''' for sponsorship reasons) is the 9th Charity Cup, an annual football match played between the winners of the [[2019 Myanmar National League|previous National League]] and [[2019 General Aung San Shield|Domestic Cup]] competitions.  It was held at [[Yangon United Sports Complex|YUSC Stadium]] on 5 January 2020. The match was played between [[Shan United F.C.|Shan United]], champions of the [[2019 Myanmar National League]] and [[Yangon United F.C.|Yangon United]], champions of the [[2019 General Aung San Shield]] <ref>{{cite web|title=\u1042\u1040\u1042\u1040 \u1018\u1031\u102c\u101c\u102f\u1036\u1038\u101b\u102c\u101e\u102e\u1021\u1000\u103c\u102d\u102f \u101b\u1014\u103a\u1015\u102f\u1036\u1004\u103d\u1031 \u1000\u103d\u1004\u103a\u1038\u1016\u103d\u1004\u1037\u103a\u1016\u101c\u102c\u1038\u1015\u103d\u1032\u1021\u1010\u103d\u1000\u103a \u1021\u1000\u103c\u102d\u102f\u100a\u103e\u102d\u1014\u103e\u102d\u102f\u1004\u103a\u1038\u1021\u1005\u100a\u103a\u1038\u1021\u101d\u1031\u1038 \u1000\u103b\u1004\u103a\u1038\u1015|url=https://themnl.com/%e1%81%82%e1%81%80%e1%81%82%e1%81%80-%e1%80%98%e1%80%b1%e1%80%ac%e1%80%9c%e1%80%af%e1%80%b6%e1%80%b8%e1%80%9b%e1%80%ac%e1%80%9e%e1%80%ae%e1%80%a1%e1%80%80%e1%80%bc%e1%80%ad%e1%80%af-%e1%80%9b%e1%80%94/|publisher=mnl|accessdate=|year=2020}}</ref>.\n\nThis was [[Yangon United F.C.|Yangon United]]'s 6th Cup appearance and [[Shan United F.C.|Shan United]]'s 4th time Cup appearance, they won Charity Cup for the first time as [[Kanbawza FC]] in 2016.\n\n==Match==\n\n===Team selection===\n\n===Details===\n{{football box\n|date=5 January 2020\n|time=16:00 [[Myanmar Standard Time|MST]]\n|team1=  [[Shan United F.C.|Shan United]]  \n|score=  2-1\n|report=  https://www.foxsportsasia.com/football/asian-football/1216513/shan-united-win-mff-charity-cup-2020-after-2-1-win-over-yangon-united/\n|team2= [[Yangon United F.C.|Yangon United]]\n|goals1=  [[Keith Martu Nah|Keith]] {{goal|57}} <br/> [[Ye Min Thu]] {{goal|74}}\n|goals2=  [[Yan Pai Soe]] {{goal|75}}\n| penaltyscore =  \n| penalties1 =  \n| penalties2 = \n|stadium=Y.U.S.C Stadium, Yangon\n|attendance= 15.000\n|referee=  {{flagicon|MYA}}  Mr. Kyaw Zwal Lwin\n}}\n{| width=92% |\n|-\n|{{Football kit\n| pattern_la   =_usa17t \n| pattern_b    = _manutd1112\n| pattern_ra   = _usa17t \n| pattern_sh = _usa17t \n| pattern_so = _usa17t\n| leftarm      = E20E0E \n|body = E20E0E \n|rightarm = E20E0E\n| socks = FF0000\n | title      = Shan United\n}}\n|{{Football kit\n| pattern_la   = _rscc0304t\n| pattern_b1    = _swans1718h\n| pattern_ra   = _rscc0304t\n| pattern_sh   = _ngra18a\n| pattern_so   = _swans1718h\n| leftarm       = FFFFFF\n| body          = FFFFFF\n| rightarm      = FFFFFF\n| shorts        = FFFFFF\n| socks         = FFFFFF\n | title      = Yangon United\n}}\n|}\n\n{| style=\"width:100%\"\n|-\n|style=\"vertical-align:top;width:50%\"|\n{| style=\"font-size:90%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"\n|-\n!width=\"25\"| !!width=\"25\"|\n|-\n|GK ||'''1'''||{{flagicon|MYA}} [[Thiha Sithu]]  ([[Captain (association football)|c]]) \n|-\n|RB ||'''4'''||{{flagicon|MYA}} [[David 